      <title>巴拿马法院批准总统领跑者的候选资格，引发债券反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/panama-court-decision-on-frontrunner-sparks-bond-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴拿马最高法院为领跑者何塞·劳尔·穆利诺 (Jose Raul Mulino) 参加周日总统选举扫清了道路，消除了市场面临的一个关键风险，随后巴拿马债券价格出现上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/panama-court-decision-on-frontrunner-sparks-bond-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 14:44:50 GMT</pubDate>
