      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 14:16:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克在选举中遭受重大打击，但不足以迫使他下台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/uk-local-elections-conservatives-hold-tees-valley-mayoralty-in-relief-for-sunak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)领导的执政保守党失去了一个领头羊议会席位，并有望解雇数百名地方议员，这是一系列毁灭性的选举结果，但仍未达到可能促使保守党罢免他的最坏情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/uk-local-elections-conservatives-hold-tees-valley-mayoralty-in-relief-for-sunak</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 11:39:26 GMT</pubDate>
